    <para id="id14157624">6/ Fourier series of a square wave — Fourier transform of square wave</para>
    <para id="id14157633">To obtain the Fourier transform of the square wave, we take the Fourier transform of one period of the square wave and multiply it by the Fourier transform of the periodic impulse train.</para>
